title: People's Court: The Case of the Greedy Babysitter
description: Jenny is bringing her boyfriend Andrew to court this week because they recently babysat his niece and he got paid for it.  Jenny thought they were doing it for free AND bought them dinner that night so she feels like Andrew should pay for the dinner.  Who's side are you on?
